WEBVTT

00:00:14.200 --> 00:00:15.470 line:80%
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

00:00:19.480 --> 00:00:24.860 line:80%
[Xiangsheng Troupe]

00:00:25.580 --> 00:00:51.950 line:80%
♪ Fires of war engulf
the frontier mountains ♪

00:00:57.150 --> 00:00:58.980 line:80%
♪ From Yao Pass
rides a young woman general ♪

00:00:59.570 --> 00:01:13.339 line:80%
♪ With delicately arched brows,
luminous eyes, and cherry-red lips ♪

00:00:59.640 --> 00:01:00.360 line:80%
Let me do it!

00:01:02.760 --> 00:01:04.030 line:80%
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

00:01:24.390 --> 00:01:27.500 line:80%
♪ Who dares say a woman
cannot rival a man? ♪

00:01:28.400 --> 00:01:30.110 line:80%
♪ The enemy general looms,
seven full feet of dread ♪

00:01:34.730 --> 00:01:36.140 line:80%
♪ She answers with a thunderous war cry ♪

00:01:39.510 --> 00:01:40.870 line:80%
Be a good pig in this life,

00:01:40.870 --> 00:01:42.930 line:80%
and be a good person in your next life.

00:01:54.870 --> 00:01:55.720 line:80%
It's done!

00:01:55.720 --> 00:01:58.779 line:80%
There's a lot of blood—
bring another basin to catch it.

00:03:33.520 --> 00:03:38.540 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:03:38.660 --> 00:03:41.350 line:80%
[Episode 1]

00:03:43.480 --> 00:03:45.270 line:80%
We'll be ready to feast in a moment.

00:03:45.270 --> 00:03:46.390 line:80%
-Great.
-Alright.

00:03:46.600 --> 00:03:47.670 line:80%
No need to rush.

00:03:51.320 --> 00:03:53.600 line:80%
Didn't the Fan family just have a funeral?

00:03:53.600 --> 00:03:55.040 line:80%
Why did Mrs. Chen

00:03:55.040 --> 00:03:57.440 line:80%
hire Changyu to slaughter
the New Year pig?

00:03:58.230 --> 00:03:59.830 line:80%
Out of pity, of course.

00:04:00.390 --> 00:04:02.520 line:80%
The Fan couple were killed by bandits,

00:04:02.550 --> 00:04:04.160 line:80%
and they left behind no property—

00:04:04.160 --> 00:04:05.760 line:80%
only two little girls.

00:04:06.430 --> 00:04:08.710 line:80%
Luckily, Changyu is capable.

00:04:09.510 --> 00:04:11.040 line:80%
She's following her father's trade,

00:04:11.040 --> 00:04:13.240 line:80%
butchering pigs to support the family.

00:04:13.270 --> 00:04:15.670 line:80%
She's held the family together
all on her own.

00:04:15.670 --> 00:04:16.840 line:80%
Poor thing.

00:04:16.840 --> 00:04:18.900 line:80%
The Fan couple were such good people.

00:04:19.069 --> 00:04:20.720 line:80%
How did they meet such a fate?

00:04:20.750 --> 00:04:21.160 line:80%
-Granny Kang.
-You're here.

00:04:21.160 --> 00:04:22.190 line:80%
Come on, sit.

00:04:22.400 --> 00:04:24.960 line:80%
It was all because of that girl.
She cursed them.

00:04:24.960 --> 00:04:25.960 line:80%
Don't talk nonsense!

00:04:25.960 --> 00:04:27.400 line:80%
Didn't I say it before?

00:04:28.310 --> 00:04:30.800 line:80%
Look at how beautiful
Fan Erniu's wife was.

00:04:31.070 --> 00:04:31.670 line:80%
Who knows,

00:04:31.910 --> 00:04:33.310 line:80%
she might have come from a brothel.

00:04:33.310 --> 00:04:36.709 line:80%
Otherwise, how would she ever marry
a butcher like Fan Erniu?

00:04:41.870 --> 00:04:43.110 line:80%
Good heavens.

00:04:43.160 --> 00:04:44.600 line:80%
Have respect for the dead.

00:04:44.600 --> 00:04:46.190 line:80%
Let's not talk about it anymore.

00:04:46.190 --> 00:04:47.360 line:80%
Am I wrong?

00:04:48.400 --> 00:04:49.800 line:80%
She may take after her mother

00:04:49.800 --> 00:04:51.530 line:80%
with all that delicate beauty,

00:04:51.870 --> 00:04:53.400 line:80%
but she has such strength.

00:04:53.870 --> 00:04:54.920 line:80%
Let alone a girl—

00:04:55.160 --> 00:04:56.400 line:80%
even a young lad

00:04:56.480 --> 00:04:57.870 line:80%
couldn't match her.

00:04:59.960 --> 00:05:01.160 line:80%
She's really strong.

00:05:02.070 --> 00:05:03.070 line:80%
That girl

00:05:03.110 --> 00:05:04.240 line:80%
just has a hard fate.

00:05:04.310 --> 00:05:05.630 line:80%
I didn't say that.

00:05:05.720 --> 00:05:07.750 line:80%
Wasn't she engaged to Song Yan?

00:05:07.960 --> 00:05:09.070 line:80%
The Song family

00:05:09.070 --> 00:05:11.160 line:80%
went to have their birth charts matched,

00:05:11.160 --> 00:05:12.920 line:80%
and when they saw the results...

00:05:12.920 --> 00:05:14.040 line:80%
oh my.

00:05:14.400 --> 00:05:17.800 line:80%
-She was born under a cursed star.
-I haven't heard of that.

00:05:18.630 --> 00:05:19.990 line:80%
The Song family panicked and hurriedly

00:05:19.990 --> 00:05:20.960 line:80%
called off the engagement.

00:05:20.960 --> 00:05:21.670 line:80%
Is that so?

00:05:23.750 --> 00:05:24.600 line:80%
Granny Kang,

00:05:24.920 --> 00:05:26.160 line:80%
here's some pig blood for you.

00:05:26.160 --> 00:05:26.960 line:80%
To help wash away your bad luck.

00:05:26.960 --> 00:05:27.960 line:80%
You... you...

00:05:29.550 --> 00:05:31.350 line:80%
Look at her! That's outrageous!

00:05:32.600 --> 00:05:33.190 line:80%
Look at what she did to me!

00:05:33.190 --> 00:05:34.360 line:80%
Mrs. Chen said

00:05:34.670 --> 00:05:37.190 line:80%
that half of today's pig
is to be shared with the neighbors.

00:05:37.190 --> 00:05:39.250 line:80%
Everyone, come and choose your cuts!

00:05:40.070 --> 00:05:41.040 line:80%
Hey, you...

00:05:41.550 --> 00:05:42.720 line:80%
Let's go, hurry.

00:05:44.430 --> 00:05:46.230 line:80%
What did I say wrong?

00:05:46.480 --> 00:05:48.550 line:80%
You... you are a jinx!

00:05:48.990 --> 00:05:50.070 line:80%
You cursed your parents to death.

00:05:50.070 --> 00:05:51.670 line:80%
-You drove your fiancé away!
-Come on, stop talking.

00:05:51.670 --> 00:05:53.520 line:80%
Your sister was born sickly—

00:05:53.520 --> 00:05:54.720 line:80%
that's also because of you!

00:05:54.720 --> 00:05:55.400 line:80%
Alright.

00:05:55.400 --> 00:05:56.360 line:80%
Well, look at her!

00:05:56.360 --> 00:05:57.750 line:80%
Granny Kang, the pork!

00:05:59.840 --> 00:06:00.430 line:80%
Don't snatch!

00:06:00.430 --> 00:06:01.720 line:80%
This piece is mine!

00:06:01.720 --> 00:06:03.190 line:80%
This piece is mine!

00:06:20.160 --> 00:06:20.990 line:80%
Changyu,

00:06:21.720 --> 00:06:23.720 line:80%
here is the money
for butchering the pig today.

00:06:23.720 --> 00:06:24.550 line:80%
Thank you, Mrs. Chen.

00:06:24.550 --> 00:06:25.840 line:80%
The feast is about to start.

00:06:25.840 --> 00:06:26.990 line:80%
Stay and eat with us.

00:06:27.550 --> 00:06:28.210 line:80%
No, thanks.

00:06:29.070 --> 00:06:30.840 line:80%
My family just had a funeral,

00:06:31.360 --> 00:06:33.600 line:80%
and you didn't mind. Hiring me anyway

00:06:34.070 --> 00:06:35.600 line:80%
was already more than kind.

00:06:36.360 --> 00:06:37.160 line:80%
Alright then.

00:06:37.720 --> 00:06:39.520 line:80%
Take the pork offal.

00:06:39.920 --> 00:06:40.920 line:80%
Oh, I couldn't.

00:06:41.630 --> 00:06:42.550 line:80%
Just take it.

00:06:43.400 --> 00:06:45.990 line:80%
Your father used to make
the best master stock.

00:06:45.990 --> 00:06:48.280 line:80%
Giving it to you won't be a waste.

00:06:48.840 --> 00:06:50.370 line:80%
Take it home for Changning.

00:06:54.400 --> 00:06:55.000 line:80%
Thank you.

00:06:55.959 --> 00:06:57.020 line:80%
I'll head back now.

00:06:57.360 --> 00:06:59.360 line:80%
Changning is waiting for me at home.

00:07:02.230 --> 00:07:02.960 line:80%
Changyu!

00:07:04.040 --> 00:07:04.920 line:80%
There's a war in Chongzhou,

00:07:04.920 --> 00:07:07.160 line:80%
so it's not peaceful around here anymore.

00:07:07.160 --> 00:07:09.110 line:80%
Be careful on your way home!

00:07:09.550 --> 00:07:10.280 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:07:10.670 --> 00:07:12.430 line:80%
I checked the almanac before leaving.

00:07:12.430 --> 00:07:13.360 line:80%
It's a lucky day.

00:07:20.310 --> 00:07:21.750 line:80%
What a good girl.

00:07:22.550 --> 00:07:23.430 line:80%
It's a pity

00:07:23.800 --> 00:07:25.400 line:80%
she has a hard life.

00:07:31.280 --> 00:07:33.800 line:80%
Four, five, six...

00:07:34.190 --> 00:07:36.990 line:80%
Ten, eleven, twelve...

00:07:37.430 --> 00:07:39.290 line:80%
Fourteen, fifteen, eighteen...

00:08:22.160 --> 00:08:23.160 line:80%
Sorry.

00:08:24.630 --> 00:08:26.870 line:80%
I'm really sorry. Sorry.

00:08:28.280 --> 00:08:30.280 line:80%
I didn't mean to. I really didn't.

00:08:30.800 --> 00:08:32.160 line:80%
You've been a good pig in this life.

00:08:32.160 --> 00:08:33.190 line:80%
Be a good person in the next life!

00:08:33.190 --> 00:08:34.310 line:80%
I didn't mean to.

00:08:34.709 --> 00:08:36.969 line:80%
Jade Emperor, Queen Mother of Heaven...

00:08:57.760 --> 00:08:58.890 line:80%
He's not breathing?

00:09:01.120 --> 00:09:02.760 line:80%
No... h-he's almost dead.

00:09:05.160 --> 00:09:05.830 line:80%
Changyu,

00:09:06.350 --> 00:09:07.310 line:80%
just go home.

00:09:12.190 --> 00:09:13.350 line:80%
No, my family is poor.

00:09:13.350 --> 00:09:14.310 line:80%
I don't have the money to save you.

00:09:14.310 --> 00:09:15.540 line:80%
I still have a younger sister at home.

00:09:15.540 --> 00:09:17.310 line:80%
What if you turn out to be a bad person?

00:09:17.310 --> 00:09:18.400 line:80%
Changyu, don't be soft-hearted.

00:09:18.400 --> 00:09:19.760 line:80%
Go home. Just go home.

00:09:19.760 --> 00:09:21.520 line:80%
Go home. Go home!

00:09:22.070 --> 00:09:23.710 line:80%
I'm coming to save you!

00:09:27.000 --> 00:09:27.800 line:80%
Don't die!

00:09:28.570 --> 00:09:29.300 line:80%
Don't die...

00:09:31.430 --> 00:09:32.560 line:80%
Don't... It's okay.

00:09:37.880 --> 00:09:39.280 line:80%
You've been a good pig in this life.

00:09:39.280 --> 00:09:41.080 line:80%
Be a good person in the next life!

00:09:55.880 --> 00:09:56.800 line:80%
Mother...

00:10:06.120 --> 00:10:08.580 line:80%
It must be my mother
who wanted me to save you.

00:10:12.400 --> 00:10:13.280 line:80%
Hold on.

00:10:13.800 --> 00:10:14.800 line:80%
Please don't die.

00:10:15.800 --> 00:10:17.530 line:80%
My mother wanted me to save you.

00:10:38.000 --> 00:10:38.920 line:80%
Changning?

00:10:40.880 --> 00:10:42.350 line:80%
Changning, open the door!

00:10:42.350 --> 00:10:43.160 line:80%
Sister,

00:10:43.800 --> 00:10:46.120 line:80%
I went to town to watch
a shadow play today.

00:10:46.120 --> 00:10:47.920 line:80%
It was about a female general...

00:10:49.190 --> 00:10:49.830 line:80%
Sister?

00:10:49.830 --> 00:10:51.630 line:80%
Help me with the things outside.

00:10:59.160 --> 00:11:00.070 line:80%
Changyu!

00:11:01.310 --> 00:11:02.510 line:80%
Who are you carrying?

00:11:02.550 --> 00:11:03.710 line:80%
I found him on the road.

00:11:03.710 --> 00:11:04.710 line:80%
He had barely a breath left in him.

00:11:04.710 --> 00:11:06.710 line:80%
Auntie Zhao, help me get him inside.

00:11:06.760 --> 00:11:07.160 line:80%
You...

00:11:07.830 --> 00:11:09.120 line:80%
You don't even know if he's good or bad,

00:11:09.120 --> 00:11:10.650 line:80%
yet you dare bring him home?

00:11:10.800 --> 00:11:11.930 line:80%
Besides, he is a man.

00:11:12.190 --> 00:11:13.710 line:80%
You're an unmarried girl.

00:11:14.120 --> 00:11:15.920 line:80%
People's gossip will drown you!

00:11:16.550 --> 00:11:18.410 line:80%
No one saw you on the way, did they?

00:11:18.470 --> 00:11:19.590 line:80%
His wounds look

00:11:20.190 --> 00:11:21.450 line:80%
just like my parents'.

00:11:21.760 --> 00:11:24.090 line:80%
He must've run into mountain bandits too.

00:11:25.280 --> 00:11:27.080 line:80%
I can't worry about all that now.

00:11:28.070 --> 00:11:29.270 line:80%
Carry him to my house.

00:11:29.760 --> 00:11:31.280 line:80%
I can't bring bad luck to your home.

00:11:31.280 --> 00:11:32.550 line:80%
What if he dies?

00:11:34.000 --> 00:11:35.000 line:80%
Either he dies out there,

00:11:35.000 --> 00:11:36.070 line:80%
or he dies in my house.

00:11:36.070 --> 00:11:36.600 line:80%
Let's go.

00:11:37.920 --> 00:11:38.880 line:80%
Come on!

00:11:43.070 --> 00:11:45.310 line:80%
My husband went to the post station
at the town entrance on business.

00:11:45.310 --> 00:11:46.350 line:80%
I have to go drag him back.

00:11:46.350 --> 00:11:47.550 line:80%
You watch him for now.

00:11:47.710 --> 00:11:48.370 line:80%
Changning,

00:11:48.470 --> 00:11:49.070 line:80%
come here!

00:11:49.640 --> 00:11:50.950 line:80%
You have to stay and watch him too.

00:11:50.950 --> 00:11:54.150 line:80%
It's improper for an unmarried girl
to be alone with a man.

00:11:54.520 --> 00:11:55.470 line:80%
I'll be back soon.

00:11:55.470 --> 00:11:56.160 line:80%
Okay.

00:12:20.070 --> 00:12:21.530 line:80%
Why is he bleeding so much?

00:12:23.310 --> 00:12:24.550 line:80%
Before Mr. Zhao gets back,

00:12:24.550 --> 00:12:26.150 line:80%
you absolutely must not die.

00:12:27.830 --> 00:12:31.360 line:80%
I've gone out to treat patients
with Mr. Zhao before, after all.

00:12:32.400 --> 00:12:34.350 line:80%
I have to try, even if it's a long shot.

00:12:34.350 --> 00:12:36.190 line:80%
Changning, go fetch a bowl of hot water.

00:12:36.190 --> 00:12:37.120 line:80%
Auntie Zhao said

00:12:37.120 --> 00:12:38.950 line:80%
an unmarried woman and a man
shouldn't be alone together.

00:12:38.950 --> 00:12:40.000 line:80%
I have to stay here and watch.

00:12:40.000 --> 00:12:41.190 line:80%
Forget about that.

00:12:41.190 --> 00:12:42.550 line:80%
He's about to die!

00:12:42.550 --> 00:12:43.280 line:80%
Go, quickly!

00:12:56.040 --> 00:12:57.880 line:80%
Last time, I used this much.

00:12:58.710 --> 00:13:00.670 line:80%
But he's bleeding more this time.

00:13:03.190 --> 00:13:04.320 line:80%
Better to add it all.

00:13:17.280 --> 00:13:18.740 line:80%
What's going on, Changyu?

00:13:19.280 --> 00:13:19.830 line:80%
He...

00:13:26.470 --> 00:13:27.550 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:13:27.590 --> 00:13:28.850 line:80%
Feeding him medicine.

00:13:29.520 --> 00:13:30.070 line:80%
You...

00:13:30.240 --> 00:13:31.470 line:80%
What the hell?

00:13:31.470 --> 00:13:33.830 line:80%
You poured the whole pack of medicine in?

00:13:33.830 --> 00:13:36.240 line:80%
Are you trying to save him or kill him?

00:13:36.240 --> 00:13:38.470 line:80%
What are you doing, kid?

00:13:40.070 --> 00:13:40.920 line:80%
I thought

00:13:41.280 --> 00:13:42.880 line:80%
since last time there wasn't
as much bleeding,

00:13:42.880 --> 00:13:44.400 line:80%
I'd use more this time.

00:13:45.880 --> 00:13:47.430 line:80%
Last time it was a donkey!

00:13:47.830 --> 00:13:48.550 line:80%
A donkey!

00:13:48.710 --> 00:13:50.310 line:80%
Is that the same as a human?

00:13:51.120 --> 00:13:53.040 line:80%
With a whole bowl of that forced down,

00:13:53.040 --> 00:13:54.040 line:80%
forget a person—

00:13:54.040 --> 00:13:56.430 line:80%
even a full-grown donkey would drop dead!

00:13:57.640 --> 00:13:59.280 line:80%
Why are you yelling?

00:14:00.280 --> 00:14:01.950 line:80%
I just wanted to save him.

00:14:02.470 --> 00:14:04.530 line:80%
I didn't want him to die in your house,

00:14:04.670 --> 00:14:06.670 line:80%
so I added a bit more medicine.

00:14:06.830 --> 00:14:08.120 line:80%
Eating too much can burst your stomach.

00:14:08.120 --> 00:14:09.550 line:80%
Then why don't you eat until you burst?

00:14:09.550 --> 00:14:11.070 line:80%
You can die from eating?

00:14:12.350 --> 00:14:13.310 line:80%
Alright, alright.

00:14:13.310 --> 00:14:14.440 line:80%
You two go out first.

00:14:14.800 --> 00:14:16.520 line:80%
Girls should wait outside.

00:14:24.830 --> 00:14:27.490 line:80%
Changyu can barely
feed herself and her sister.

00:14:27.640 --> 00:14:29.310 line:80%
What is she thinking,
bringing a strange man home?

00:14:29.310 --> 00:14:31.160 line:80%
Why didn't you stop her?

00:14:32.590 --> 00:14:33.800 line:80%
Look at that face,

00:14:33.800 --> 00:14:34.710 line:80%
and you'll know why.

00:14:34.710 --> 00:14:35.840 line:80%
How could I stop her?

00:14:35.880 --> 00:14:37.430 line:80%
What use is a pretty face?

00:14:37.710 --> 00:14:39.510 line:80%
It doesn't put food on the table.

00:14:53.040 --> 00:14:55.280 line:80%
That big brother is so handsome.

00:14:55.430 --> 00:14:57.640 line:80%
That's why you carried him back, right?

00:14:58.470 --> 00:14:59.310 line:80%
Nonsense.

00:14:59.590 --> 00:15:01.190 line:80%
I was just trying to save him.

00:15:01.470 --> 00:15:03.400 line:80%
It has nothing to do with his looks.

00:15:37.310 --> 00:15:40.190 line:80%
The scouts have tracked them
all the way here from Chongzhou.

00:15:40.190 --> 00:15:42.320 line:80%
The blood trail disappeared here too.

00:15:42.430 --> 00:15:43.760 line:80%
It snowed for a day and a night,

00:15:43.760 --> 00:15:45.690 line:80%
so the footprints are all covered.

00:15:46.550 --> 00:15:47.800 line:80%
This is Jizhou.

00:15:46.870 --> 00:15:51.970 line:80%
[Wei Sheng]

00:15:48.000 --> 00:15:49.590 line:80%
He Jingyuan's turf.

00:15:50.280 --> 00:15:52.350 line:80%
We cannot search without permission.

00:15:52.350 --> 00:15:54.640 line:80%
Report this back to the capital.
Let the Prime Minister decide.

00:15:54.640 --> 00:15:55.240 line:80%
Let's head back.

00:15:55.240 --> 00:15:55.790 line:80%
Yes, sir.

00:15:55.810 --> 00:15:56.350 line:80%
Yes, sir.

00:16:05.310 --> 00:16:09.040 line:80%
[Chunfeng Tofu Shop]

00:16:17.490 --> 00:16:24.770 line:80%
[Xigu Lane]

00:16:24.160 --> 00:16:25.420 line:80%
Changyu, you're back.

00:16:26.000 --> 00:16:26.710 line:80%
Changyu.

00:16:29.590 --> 00:16:30.590 line:80%
Changyu!

00:16:30.590 --> 00:16:32.040 line:80%
Changyu, please wait!

00:16:36.640 --> 00:16:37.710 line:80%
Changyu.

00:16:40.160 --> 00:16:41.640 line:80%
Haven't seen you in half a month,

00:16:41.640 --> 00:16:44.470 line:80%
and you've only grown more beautiful.

00:16:46.240 --> 00:16:46.840 line:80%
This is...

00:16:47.520 --> 00:16:51.190 line:80%
This is the medicine
you just bought for Changning?

00:16:51.400 --> 00:16:52.160 line:80%
I have some...

00:16:52.160 --> 00:16:53.760 line:80%
Just say what you want to say.

00:16:55.040 --> 00:16:56.430 line:80%
I was just thinking

00:16:56.920 --> 00:16:58.450 line:80%
your engagement with my son

00:16:58.470 --> 00:16:59.950 line:80%
was already called off.

00:17:00.350 --> 00:17:03.310 line:80%
So, it's useless for you
to keep that betrothal letter.

00:17:03.310 --> 00:17:05.909 line:80%
-How about...
-You want the betrothal letter?

00:17:06.629 --> 00:17:07.389 line:80%
Fine.

00:17:08.040 --> 00:17:09.520 line:80%
Let's settle the accounts first.

00:17:09.520 --> 00:17:12.720 line:80%
Over these years, my family paid
tuition fees for Song Yan

00:17:12.909 --> 00:17:14.970 line:80%
and gave financial aid to both of you—

00:17:15.310 --> 00:17:16.629 line:80%
settle those accounts,

00:17:16.629 --> 00:17:18.159 line:80%
and I'll return the letter.

00:17:18.350 --> 00:17:21.149 line:80%
You can't blame us
for calling off the engagement.

00:17:21.200 --> 00:17:23.730 line:80%
That fortune teller said
your fate is cursed!

00:17:23.909 --> 00:17:25.310 line:80%
I can't let my Yan marry a woman like you

00:17:25.310 --> 00:17:27.440 line:80%
who brings misfortune to her husband!

00:17:27.909 --> 00:17:29.440 line:80%
If we're talking about debts,

00:17:29.440 --> 00:17:31.150 line:80%
we owe your parents,

00:17:31.350 --> 00:17:32.760 line:80%
not you.

00:17:33.200 --> 00:17:35.070 line:80%
My father signed that betrothal letter
with you.

00:17:35.070 --> 00:17:37.590 line:80%
Then go down to the underworld
and ask him yourself.

00:17:37.590 --> 00:17:38.650 line:80%
You wretched girl!

00:17:39.280 --> 00:17:40.280 line:80%
Stop right there!

00:17:40.280 --> 00:17:40.800 line:80%
Mother.

00:17:47.870 --> 00:17:48.870 line:80%
Please calm down.

00:17:49.910 --> 00:17:50.770 line:80%
It's better...

00:17:53.440 --> 00:17:55.350 line:80%
if I explain things to her.

00:17:57.550 --> 00:17:58.800 line:80%
Yan,

00:17:59.070 --> 00:18:00.520 line:80%
that wretched girl...

00:18:00.630 --> 00:18:02.690 line:80%
she's just after your official rank.

00:18:02.910 --> 00:18:05.550 line:80%
She knows you're soft-hearted
and easy to manipulate.

00:18:05.550 --> 00:18:07.280 line:80%
That's why she won't let you go.

00:18:07.350 --> 00:18:10.310 line:80%
She's using past favors
to demand repayment!

00:18:12.040 --> 00:18:12.800 line:80%
In a few days,

00:18:12.800 --> 00:18:13.760 line:80%
-Using past favors...
-the County Magistrate

00:18:13.760 --> 00:18:15.000 line:80%
will come to escort us to our new home.

00:18:15.000 --> 00:18:15.680 line:80%
To demand repayment?

00:18:15.680 --> 00:18:16.200 line:80%
-Mother.
-By then,

00:18:16.200 --> 00:18:18.400 line:80%
-she'll pay for this.
-Let's go inside.

00:18:27.280 --> 00:18:27.960 line:80%
Changyu,

00:18:28.800 --> 00:18:31.060 line:80%
I, Song Yan, am not an ungrateful person.

00:18:31.950 --> 00:18:34.680 line:80%
I have always remembered
your family's kindness.

00:18:34.680 --> 00:18:36.350 line:80%
But of all virtues,
filial piety comes first.

00:18:36.350 --> 00:18:38.390 line:80%
If I defied my mother
and insisted on marrying you,

00:18:38.390 --> 00:18:40.850 line:80%
I'd become an unfilial
and unrighteous man.

00:18:41.910 --> 00:18:43.350 line:80%
Although we cannot
become husband and wife,

00:18:43.350 --> 00:18:44.960 line:80%
we can be like brother and sister.

00:18:44.960 --> 00:18:46.550 line:80%
I'll take what you just said

00:18:46.870 --> 00:18:48.040 line:80%
as mere words spoken in anger.

00:18:48.040 --> 00:18:49.150 line:80%
I won't take them to heart.

00:18:49.150 --> 00:18:49.720 line:80%
Don't.

00:18:50.800 --> 00:18:52.550 line:80%
You must take them to heart.

00:18:53.070 --> 00:18:55.730 line:80%
And there's no need
to speak of being my brother.

00:18:55.800 --> 00:18:58.310 line:80%
Even between real brothers,
accounts must be clear.

00:18:58.310 --> 00:18:59.720 line:80%
What I hate most

00:19:00.440 --> 00:19:02.900 line:80%
are those who gossip
behind people's backs,

00:19:03.390 --> 00:19:05.250 line:80%
spreading rumors that I'm a jinx,

00:19:05.680 --> 00:19:07.680 line:80%
that my family is trading favors
for marriage,

00:19:07.680 --> 00:19:09.940 line:80%
and that I'm forcing Song Yan to marry me!

00:19:10.520 --> 00:19:11.910 line:80%
Others said those things!

00:19:11.910 --> 00:19:13.110 line:80%
What does that have to do with us?

00:19:13.110 --> 00:19:14.630 line:80%
I never mentioned your name,

00:19:14.630 --> 00:19:16.680 line:80%
so why are you in such a rush to admit it?

00:19:16.680 --> 00:19:18.000 line:80%
-You wretched girl...
-Mother!

00:19:18.000 --> 00:19:18.590 line:80%
Changyu,

00:19:19.000 --> 00:19:20.800 line:80%
I don't care what outsiders think.

00:19:20.800 --> 00:19:22.720 line:80%
But the feelings between us
all these years—

00:19:22.720 --> 00:19:24.590 line:80%
can they truly be weighed only in
silver and gold?

00:19:24.590 --> 00:19:26.720 line:80%
Yes, they can only be weighed that way!

00:19:28.110 --> 00:19:31.110 line:80%
You give me the money,
and I give you the betrothal letter.

00:19:31.110 --> 00:19:33.710 line:80%
Don't disgust me with your talk
of "feelings."

00:19:33.800 --> 00:19:35.870 line:80%
Raising two pigs would have been better
than knowing you!

00:19:35.870 --> 00:19:36.590 line:80%
You...

00:19:38.680 --> 00:19:40.240 line:80%
are nothing but ingrates.

00:19:41.000 --> 00:19:42.310 line:80%
What did you say?

00:19:43.040 --> 00:19:44.150 line:80%
You wretched girl,

00:19:44.280 --> 00:19:45.800 line:80%
watch your mouth!

00:19:45.800 --> 00:19:47.040 line:80%
-You are a pig!
-Mother.

00:19:47.040 --> 00:19:48.630 line:80%
-Your whole family are pigs!
-Mother.

00:19:48.630 --> 00:19:50.290 line:80%
No wonder you slaughter pigs!

00:19:50.590 --> 00:19:51.960 line:80%
What nonsense is this?

00:19:53.550 --> 00:19:54.910 line:80%
The old saying is right—

00:19:55.680 --> 00:19:56.880 line:80%
spending money on men

00:19:57.070 --> 00:19:58.720 line:80%
only invites divine punishment.

00:19:58.720 --> 00:20:01.070 line:80%
There's still a man lying in the room!

00:20:02.720 --> 00:20:03.650 line:80%
You startled me.

00:20:06.910 --> 00:20:07.240 line:80%
Here.

00:20:08.310 --> 00:20:09.800 line:80%
Those packs must have cost enough

00:20:09.800 --> 00:20:11.730 line:80%
to attract divine punishment, eh?

00:20:14.280 --> 00:20:14.960 line:80%
Changyu.

00:20:15.910 --> 00:20:16.720 line:80%
That young man is awake.

00:20:16.720 --> 00:20:18.200 line:80%
Go and check on him.

00:20:18.800 --> 00:20:19.680 line:80%
Really?

00:20:20.760 --> 00:20:22.310 line:80%
I thought he was a goner!

00:20:22.830 --> 00:20:24.290 line:80%
Mr. Zhao, you're amazing!

00:20:24.390 --> 00:20:27.250 line:80%
You're a miracle worker
for all sorts of creatures!

00:20:30.350 --> 00:20:31.350 line:80%
Is that a compliment

00:20:31.350 --> 00:20:32.390 line:80%
or a jab?

00:20:40.800 --> 00:20:41.680 line:80%
You're awake.

00:21:09.630 --> 00:21:10.310 line:80%
I...

00:21:10.800 --> 00:21:12.530 line:80%
I saw you collapsed in the snow,

00:21:12.830 --> 00:21:14.310 line:80%
so I carried you back.

00:21:15.000 --> 00:21:16.870 line:80%
But the one who truly saved you
from death's door

00:21:16.870 --> 00:21:17.760 line:80%
is Mr. Zhao.

00:21:20.720 --> 00:21:22.320 line:80%
He changed your clothes too.

00:21:25.630 --> 00:21:26.630 line:80%
This is his home.

00:21:28.550 --> 00:21:29.680 line:80%
He is a doctor.

00:21:30.000 --> 00:21:31.550 line:80%
He treats mules and horses.

00:21:33.280 --> 00:21:34.760 line:80%
People too, of course.

00:21:41.000 --> 00:21:41.830 line:80%
Thank you.

00:21:44.200 --> 00:21:45.720 line:80%
When you carried me back,

00:21:46.830 --> 00:21:48.310 line:80%
did you see anyone else?

00:21:48.550 --> 00:21:49.520 line:80%
Anyone else?

00:21:51.310 --> 00:21:52.630 line:80%
No, it was just you.

00:21:52.760 --> 00:21:55.220 line:80%
There were others
buried in that snowdrift?

00:22:11.680 --> 00:22:13.010 line:80%
I'll get you some water.

00:22:14.680 --> 00:22:15.110 line:80%
Here.

00:22:18.870 --> 00:22:20.240 line:80%
Where am I?

00:22:23.070 --> 00:22:25.800 line:80%
This is Xigu Lane, Lin'an Town,
Qingping County.

00:22:26.760 --> 00:22:28.960 line:80%
You don't look like
you're from around here.

00:22:28.960 --> 00:22:30.020 line:80%
Where are you from?

00:22:30.280 --> 00:22:31.110 line:80%
What's your name?

00:22:31.110 --> 00:22:32.590 line:80%
Did you run into bandits?

00:22:37.960 --> 00:22:39.000 line:80%
I'm Yan Zheng.

00:22:40.390 --> 00:22:41.720 line:80%
"Yan" stands for words,

00:22:42.240 --> 00:22:44.040 line:80%
and "Zheng" for righteousness.

00:22:44.390 --> 00:22:47.200 line:80%
I fled here as a refugee from Chongzhou.

00:22:51.040 --> 00:22:52.640 line:80%
Do you have any other family?

00:23:15.550 --> 00:23:16.590 line:80%
All Solus.

00:23:18.200 --> 00:23:19.240 line:80%
"All Solus"?

00:23:20.760 --> 00:23:22.560 line:80%
Your family isn't surnamed Yan?

00:23:22.960 --> 00:23:24.760 line:80%
Is "All Solus" your stepfather?

00:23:28.310 --> 00:23:29.520 line:80%
I mean,

00:23:29.830 --> 00:23:31.690 line:80%
I'm the only one left in my family.

00:23:34.520 --> 00:23:35.440 line:80%
I'm sorry.

00:23:36.480 --> 00:23:38.150 line:80%
No wonder when I saved you,

00:23:38.910 --> 00:23:40.770 line:80%
you kept calling for your mother.

00:23:56.110 --> 00:23:57.000 line:80%
Mr. Zhao!

00:23:57.480 --> 00:23:58.390 line:80%
What's wrong? What's wrong?

00:23:58.390 --> 00:23:59.990 line:80%
Why is he coughing like this?

00:24:00.310 --> 00:24:01.200 line:80%
I don't know.

00:24:01.310 --> 00:24:02.110 line:80%
I just mentioned his mother,

00:24:02.110 --> 00:24:03.350 line:80%
and he started coughing!

00:24:03.350 --> 00:24:05.080 line:80%
Why did you bring up his mother?

00:24:05.390 --> 00:24:07.830 line:80%
You can't upset the patient
at a time like this.

00:24:07.830 --> 00:24:08.870 line:80%
Oh, holy mother.

00:24:09.280 --> 00:24:10.740 line:80%
You just mentioned it too.

00:24:13.390 --> 00:24:14.240 line:80%
Look!

00:24:14.240 --> 00:24:16.170 line:80%
Quick, help him lie down properly.

00:24:19.280 --> 00:24:20.110 line:80%
Yan Zheng?

00:24:20.800 --> 00:24:21.800 line:80%
Yan Zheng?

00:24:22.200 --> 00:24:23.040 line:80%
Yan Zheng?

00:24:24.250 --> 00:24:29.380 line:80%
[Yan]

00:24:26.110 --> 00:24:28.440 line:80%
If he really dies because of my questions,

00:24:28.550 --> 00:24:29.520 line:80%
what should I do?

00:24:30.520 --> 00:24:32.450 line:80%
Even a simple coffin is expensive.

00:24:34.040 --> 00:24:34.910 line:80%
How about

00:24:35.590 --> 00:24:37.120 line:80%
I just dig a pit and bury him?

00:24:37.550 --> 00:24:38.390 line:80%
Changyu,

00:24:38.590 --> 00:24:40.960 line:80%
how about we ask the Heavens?

00:24:42.590 --> 00:24:43.280 line:80%
That works.

00:24:44.240 --> 00:24:46.240 line:80%
Good or bad, let the Heavens decide.

00:24:46.390 --> 00:24:48.450 line:80%
Let's play the straw-snapping game.

00:24:50.680 --> 00:24:52.630 line:80%
If I lose, I'll buy a coffin.

00:24:52.960 --> 00:24:54.630 line:80%
If you lose, I'll dig a pit.

00:24:54.630 --> 00:24:55.280 line:80%
Okay.

00:25:00.830 --> 00:25:02.030 line:80%
Best two out of three.

00:25:05.150 --> 00:25:06.410 line:80%
Three rounds maximum.

00:25:06.590 --> 00:25:07.110 line:80%
Again.

00:25:10.480 --> 00:25:12.000 line:80%
The Heavens said three times,

00:25:12.000 --> 00:25:13.110 line:80%
"Buy a coffin."

00:25:13.590 --> 00:25:15.150 line:80%
My money pouch says...

00:25:17.150 --> 00:25:17.830 line:80%
dig a pit.

00:25:28.910 --> 00:25:29.720 line:80%
Mr. Zhao.

00:25:30.200 --> 00:25:32.270 line:80%
Don't blame yourself
if you can't save him.

00:25:32.270 --> 00:25:33.480 line:80%
It's his own fate.

00:25:36.590 --> 00:25:37.550 line:80%
What is this?

00:25:38.960 --> 00:25:40.440 line:80%
My sister is stingy.

00:25:40.440 --> 00:25:43.900 line:80%
The Heavens told her to buy a coffin
for that handsome brother,

00:25:43.960 --> 00:25:45.870 line:80%
but she insists on
digging a pit just to get by.

00:25:45.870 --> 00:25:47.330 line:80%
I'm not just "getting by."

00:25:47.440 --> 00:25:48.850 line:80%
I even made him a memorial tablet.

00:25:48.850 --> 00:25:50.260 line:80%
Look, "Yan Zheng."

00:25:51.020 --> 00:25:51.700 line:80%
Luckily,

00:25:51.960 --> 00:25:53.960 line:80%
I know how to write both characters.

00:25:56.280 --> 00:25:58.720 line:80%
Throw this unlucky thing away immediately!

00:25:58.720 --> 00:26:01.050 line:80%
That young man has a strong constitution.

00:26:01.830 --> 00:26:02.910 line:80%
Plus, last night

00:26:03.040 --> 00:26:04.960 line:80%
you fed him some hemostatic decoction,

00:26:04.960 --> 00:26:06.520 line:80%
and he coughed up
a mouthful of clotted blood.

00:26:06.520 --> 00:26:08.150 line:80%
His life is saved!

00:26:08.480 --> 00:26:09.760 line:80%
That's great!

00:26:10.280 --> 00:26:11.240 line:80%
His life is saved!

00:26:11.240 --> 00:26:13.830 line:80%
His life is saved. His life is saved.

00:26:13.910 --> 00:26:15.680 line:80%
Don't celebrate too early, you two.

00:26:15.680 --> 00:26:17.140 line:80%
From here on, the medicine

00:26:17.150 --> 00:26:18.950 line:80%
will cost more than that coffin.

00:26:19.760 --> 00:26:20.520 line:80%
Changning.

00:26:21.680 --> 00:26:22.440 line:80%
We're having noodles tonight.

00:26:22.440 --> 00:26:23.370 line:80%
Go to the kitchen

00:26:23.760 --> 00:26:25.440 line:80%
and fetch me half a basin of master sauce.

00:26:25.440 --> 00:26:26.280 line:80%
Okay.

00:26:29.480 --> 00:26:31.040 line:80%
Changyu, come here.

00:26:34.280 --> 00:26:35.910 line:80%
What are you thinking?

00:26:37.480 --> 00:26:39.110 line:80%
Changning has always been in poor health

00:26:39.110 --> 00:26:40.300 line:80%
and is still taking medicine.

00:26:40.300 --> 00:26:42.760 line:80%
Where will you get the extra money
for his medicine?

00:26:42.760 --> 00:26:43.870 line:80%
Does that young man

00:26:44.150 --> 00:26:45.870 line:80%
have any family left?

00:26:46.830 --> 00:26:47.910 line:80%
He's "all Solus."

00:26:49.350 --> 00:26:50.680 line:80%
-He's what?
-He's what?

00:26:52.310 --> 00:26:54.040 line:80%
He said his whole family is dead.

00:26:54.040 --> 00:26:55.300 line:80%
He's the only one left.

00:26:55.590 --> 00:26:57.190 line:80%
He fled here from Chongzhou.

00:26:57.550 --> 00:26:59.800 line:80%
He ran into bandits at Huchakou.

00:27:00.310 --> 00:27:01.280 line:80%
Right now,

00:27:02.200 --> 00:27:04.200 line:80%
I'm afraid he has nowhere else to go.

00:27:04.390 --> 00:27:05.480 line:80%
Does he have

00:27:05.720 --> 00:27:07.240 line:80%
any money on him

00:27:07.240 --> 00:27:08.390 line:80%
or a travel permit?

00:27:08.760 --> 00:27:09.910 line:80%
When I changed his clothes,

00:27:09.910 --> 00:27:10.630 line:80%
I checked everything.

00:27:10.630 --> 00:27:11.630 line:80%
Not a single coin.

00:27:12.190 --> 00:27:13.060 line:80%
Either

00:27:13.480 --> 00:27:15.150 line:80%
the bandits robbed him clean,

00:27:15.390 --> 00:27:17.200 line:80%
or he's just a pauper himself.

00:27:21.150 --> 00:27:23.240 line:80%
How about we carry him to
the county government office?

00:27:23.240 --> 00:27:25.240 line:80%
Let the officials decide what to do.

00:27:25.440 --> 00:27:26.000 line:80%
No way.

00:27:26.310 --> 00:27:28.070 line:80%
There are so many beggars
lying outside that office.

00:27:28.070 --> 00:27:29.480 line:80%
Have you ever seen them care?

00:27:29.480 --> 00:27:30.280 line:80%
That's right.

00:27:30.910 --> 00:27:33.040 line:80%
If he were dead, we could just bury him.

00:27:33.200 --> 00:27:35.860 line:80%
But since he's alive,
we can't just abandon him.

00:27:38.720 --> 00:27:40.200 line:80%
Let him recover here first.

00:27:40.200 --> 00:27:41.150 line:80%
As for money,

00:27:41.910 --> 00:27:43.440 line:80%
I'll figure something out.

00:27:50.670 --> 00:27:55.990 line:80%
[Xigu Lane]

00:27:53.520 --> 00:27:56.150 line:80%
The weather is dry.

00:27:57.040 --> 00:27:59.830 line:80%
Beware of fire hazards!

00:27:59.540 --> 00:28:04.620 line:80%
[Fill Your Belly]

00:28:06.220 --> 00:28:11.000 line:80%
[Fill Your Belly]

00:28:15.280 --> 00:28:18.870 line:80%
Two, four, six, eight, ten.

00:28:21.760 --> 00:28:23.550 line:80%
Five, ten, eleven...

00:28:44.630 --> 00:28:45.390 line:80%
Mother,

00:28:46.110 --> 00:28:48.510 line:80%
if it's really you
who wanted me to save him,

00:28:48.910 --> 00:28:50.770 line:80%
should I see it through to the end?

00:28:57.590 --> 00:28:58.870 line:80%
What should I do?

00:29:38.850 --> 00:29:42.110 line:80%
[Lin'an]

00:29:42.260 --> 00:29:44.830 line:80%
[Luo's Pawnshop]

00:29:43.870 --> 00:29:44.910 line:80%
One tael?

00:29:45.480 --> 00:29:47.440 line:80%
This hairpin is made of pure silver!

00:29:47.440 --> 00:29:49.310 line:80%
My father spent almost four taels on it!

00:29:49.310 --> 00:29:51.370 line:80%
Well, this hairpin is indeed silver,

00:29:51.590 --> 00:29:54.110 line:80%
but I can only give you
one tael and five mace.

00:29:54.520 --> 00:29:56.680 line:80%
If it weren't for
what happened to your family,

00:29:56.680 --> 00:29:58.870 line:80%
you wouldn't get
any more than this anywhere...

00:29:58.870 --> 00:29:59.440 line:80%
Wait...

00:29:59.440 --> 00:30:00.070 line:80%
Wait, wait, wait!

00:30:00.070 --> 00:30:01.040 line:80%
Don't go!

00:30:01.390 --> 00:30:03.000 line:80%
We can still negotiate.

00:30:07.350 --> 00:30:08.070 line:80%
Two taels!

00:30:08.720 --> 00:30:09.870 line:80%
Not one coin less!

00:30:11.680 --> 00:30:12.810 line:80%
Alright, come back.

00:30:13.310 --> 00:30:15.830 line:80%
Since we're neighbors in Xigu Lane,

00:30:16.030 --> 00:30:17.890 line:80%
I'll do it to earn some good karma.

00:30:18.720 --> 00:30:20.250 line:80%
Put your fingerprint here.

00:30:21.070 --> 00:30:22.600 line:80%
I'll definitely redeem it.

00:30:23.110 --> 00:30:24.570 line:80%
It's very important to me.

00:30:24.590 --> 00:30:25.760 line:80%
Rest assured.

00:30:32.130 --> 00:30:35.590 line:80%
[One silver hairpin pledged.
Two taels of silver granted.]

00:30:43.150 --> 00:30:44.760 line:80%
As if it were a rare treasure.

00:30:48.760 --> 00:30:49.280 line:80%
Go.

00:30:50.000 --> 00:30:50.760 line:80%
Changyu,

00:30:51.390 --> 00:30:52.320 line:80%
you bought pigs.

00:30:52.960 --> 00:30:55.090 line:80%
Fan's Butcher Shop reopens tomorrow.

00:30:55.590 --> 00:30:57.720 line:80%
Everyone, please come and support us!

00:30:57.720 --> 00:30:58.520 line:80%
She's the boss now.

00:30:58.520 --> 00:30:59.520 line:80%
Sure, sure.

00:31:00.830 --> 00:31:01.440 line:80%
Changyu!

00:31:03.390 --> 00:31:03.960 line:80%
Mr. Li?

00:31:04.480 --> 00:31:05.240 line:80%
Are you...

00:31:05.680 --> 00:31:07.350 line:80%
taking over your father's business?

00:31:07.350 --> 00:31:09.080 line:80%
I have to make a living, don't I?

00:31:09.310 --> 00:31:10.370 line:80%
That's the spirit.

00:31:10.480 --> 00:31:11.590 line:80%
Don't listen to what others say.

00:31:10.600 --> 00:31:15.610 line:80%
[Li Deqin, Chef of Yixiang Restaurant]

00:31:11.800 --> 00:31:12.840 line:80%
What's wrong with butchering pigs?

00:31:12.840 --> 00:31:14.110 line:80%
Food makes no distinction
between men and women,

00:31:14.110 --> 00:31:15.640 line:80%
and neither does hard work.

00:31:16.070 --> 00:31:16.870 line:80%
Thank you, Mr. Li.

00:31:16.870 --> 00:31:17.440 line:80%
Look.

00:31:17.800 --> 00:31:19.280 line:80%
I used the pig-selecting method
my father taught me

00:31:19.280 --> 00:31:20.480 line:80%
to choose these pigs.

00:31:20.760 --> 00:31:22.890 line:80%
Look at this round rump and short tail.

00:31:23.070 --> 00:31:25.000 line:80%
Pigs like this
have thick skin and rich fat.

00:31:25.000 --> 00:31:26.830 line:80%
It will be top-quality pork!

00:31:26.830 --> 00:31:27.910 line:80%
Since it's going to be top-quality pork,

00:31:27.910 --> 00:31:29.280 line:80%
how could we not fight for it?

00:31:29.280 --> 00:31:31.110 line:80%
Our Yixiang Restaurant
will order half a side!

00:31:31.110 --> 00:31:32.070 line:80%
Thanks, Mr. Li!

00:31:32.520 --> 00:31:33.650 line:80%
-Bye, Mr. Li!
-Okay!

00:31:34.200 --> 00:31:34.730 line:80%
Let's go.

00:31:35.110 --> 00:31:35.630 line:80%
Go.

00:31:37.760 --> 00:31:38.760 line:80%
Shoo, shoo, shoo.

00:31:38.910 --> 00:31:39.910 line:80%
Shoo, shoo, shoo.

00:31:40.240 --> 00:31:41.800 line:80%
-Shoo, shoo, shoo.
-Changyu!

00:31:41.800 --> 00:31:42.720 line:80%
Back from buying pigs?

00:31:42.720 --> 00:31:43.200 line:80%
Yes.

00:31:43.200 --> 00:31:44.200 line:80%
This pig is so fat.

00:31:45.390 --> 00:31:46.440 line:80%
Shoo, shoo, shoo...

00:31:46.440 --> 00:31:47.000 line:80%
Shoo...

00:31:55.480 --> 00:31:56.680 line:80%
Good little piggies.

00:31:57.480 --> 00:31:58.590 line:80%
Let's not block the way.

00:31:58.590 --> 00:31:59.480 line:80%
Let's go.

00:32:05.480 --> 00:32:06.310 line:80%
Come on. Move!

00:32:06.390 --> 00:32:06.920 line:80%
Hurry up!

00:32:07.110 --> 00:32:08.630 line:80%
Go. Get going. Go.

00:32:10.350 --> 00:32:10.910 line:80%
Come on.

00:32:11.960 --> 00:32:12.960 line:80%
Shoo, shoo, shoo.

00:32:13.680 --> 00:32:14.480 line:80%
Let's go home.

00:32:56.680 --> 00:33:00.410 line:80%
[Are you alright? Please reply promptly.]

00:33:05.610 --> 00:33:07.190 line:80%
[Are you alright? Please reply promptly.]

00:33:33.270 --> 00:33:35.240 line:80%
[Xigu Lane, Lin'an Town, Qingping County]

00:34:19.510 --> 00:34:21.039 line:80%
A white-feathered falcon?

00:34:38.080 --> 00:34:39.160 line:80%
Who threw this?

00:34:39.470 --> 00:34:40.530 line:80%
It hurts like hell!

00:34:48.680 --> 00:34:50.410 line:80%
Where did this stone come from?

00:34:51.310 --> 00:34:52.830 line:80%
Which bastard hit me?

00:34:53.680 --> 00:34:55.280 line:80%
I'll kill him!

00:34:55.510 --> 00:34:56.080 line:80%
Let's go!

00:34:58.030 --> 00:34:59.390 line:80%
You really haven't seen any?

00:34:59.390 --> 00:35:00.760 line:80%
No, I am from this village.

00:35:00.760 --> 00:35:01.830 line:80%
Anyone found sheltering refugees...

00:35:01.830 --> 00:35:02.640 line:80%
will be imprisoned.

00:35:02.640 --> 00:35:03.640 line:80%
Report truthfully.

00:35:03.640 --> 00:35:03.990 line:80%
Rest assured, sir.

00:35:03.990 --> 00:35:05.720 line:80%
-Check over there.
-Of course.

00:35:09.430 --> 00:35:10.560 line:80%
-What happened?
-Cut the crap!

00:35:10.560 --> 00:35:12.080 line:80%
How many households are left?

00:35:12.080 --> 00:35:12.600 line:80%
Sir,

00:35:12.870 --> 00:35:15.510 line:80%
should I take you to a doctor first?

00:35:15.510 --> 00:35:16.430 line:80%
To hell with the doctor!

00:35:16.430 --> 00:35:17.470 line:80%
You guys check the households ahead!

00:35:17.470 --> 00:35:18.130 line:80%
-Yes!
-Yes!

00:35:26.350 --> 00:35:27.990 line:80%
Sir, what's going on?

00:35:28.350 --> 00:35:29.760 line:80%
They're going door to door,

00:35:29.760 --> 00:35:33.560 line:80%
searching for refugees
without household registration document.

00:35:34.280 --> 00:35:35.140 line:80%
That scared me.

00:35:35.430 --> 00:35:37.760 line:80%
I thought they were collecting grain tax.

00:35:39.160 --> 00:35:40.990 line:80%
Why the sudden check for refugees?

00:35:40.990 --> 00:35:42.390 line:80%
They're going to arrest all the refugees

00:35:42.390 --> 00:35:44.350 line:80%
and send them to
the Chongzhou battlefield.

00:35:44.350 --> 00:35:45.680 line:80%
The war there is critical.

00:35:45.680 --> 00:35:48.510 line:80%
Once taken, they'll be placed in
the vanguard battalion.

00:35:48.510 --> 00:35:49.870 line:80%
What's the vanguard battalion?

00:35:49.870 --> 00:35:51.000 line:80%
Is that impressive?

00:35:51.200 --> 00:35:52.390 line:80%
They're sent to die.

00:36:10.600 --> 00:36:11.200 line:80%
Yan Zheng,

00:36:11.680 --> 00:36:15.280 line:80%
do you have a travel permit
or household registration document?

00:36:17.910 --> 00:36:18.510 line:80%
Yes.

00:36:20.640 --> 00:36:21.510 line:80%
But I lost them.

00:36:22.600 --> 00:36:23.400 line:80%
You lost them?

00:36:24.800 --> 00:36:25.950 line:80%
Look for them again.

00:36:26.720 --> 00:36:27.870 line:80%
Have you checked your clothes?

00:36:27.870 --> 00:36:29.470 line:80%
When you changed my clothes,

00:36:29.510 --> 00:36:31.350 line:80%
didn't you go through everything on me?

00:36:31.350 --> 00:36:31.910 line:80%
I...

00:36:35.310 --> 00:36:36.950 line:80%
I did that to save you.

00:36:37.240 --> 00:36:38.510 line:80%
Don't misunderstand.

00:36:40.310 --> 00:36:41.570 line:80%
Wait, how did you know?

00:36:41.910 --> 00:36:42.510 line:80%
You...

00:36:44.510 --> 00:36:46.470 line:80%
This isn't the time to talk about this.

00:36:46.470 --> 00:36:47.830 line:80%
If you don't have a travel permit
or household registration document,

00:36:47.830 --> 00:36:49.030 line:80%
you'll be taken as a refugee

00:36:49.030 --> 00:36:51.360 line:80%
and sent to die in the vanguard battalion!

00:36:56.200 --> 00:36:57.200 line:80%
What should we do?

00:36:57.390 --> 00:36:58.790 line:80%
The soldiers are coming.

00:36:59.350 --> 00:37:00.950 line:80%
Since the soldiers are here,

00:37:01.760 --> 00:37:03.420 line:80%
I can't stay and cause trouble

00:37:03.800 --> 00:37:04.910 line:80%
for you.

00:37:16.350 --> 00:37:17.280 line:80%
I've got an idea.

00:37:18.830 --> 00:37:20.160 line:80%
There's a place to hide.

00:37:22.120 --> 00:37:22.920 line:80%
Open the door.

00:37:23.990 --> 00:37:24.680 line:80%
Open up!

00:37:25.760 --> 00:37:26.560 line:80%
Open the door!

00:37:32.160 --> 00:37:34.020 line:80%
Community Head, what's going on?

00:37:37.080 --> 00:37:37.830 line:80%
Changyu,

00:37:38.350 --> 00:37:39.870 line:80%
are you the only one home?

00:37:41.760 --> 00:37:43.720 line:80%
Sir, this is the Fan's household.

00:37:44.600 --> 00:37:47.000 line:80%
It's connected to the Zhao family's place.

00:37:49.120 --> 00:37:51.250 line:80%
Are there any strangers staying here?

00:37:51.800 --> 00:37:52.560 line:80%
No.

00:37:53.200 --> 00:37:54.430 line:80%
It's a small town.

00:37:54.830 --> 00:37:56.910 line:80%
Everyone knows each other.

00:37:57.640 --> 00:37:59.600 line:80%
We'd notice
even an extra stray cat or dog.

00:37:59.600 --> 00:38:01.060 line:80%
There's no stranger here.

00:38:03.080 --> 00:38:03.560 line:80%
No one.

00:38:06.080 --> 00:38:07.010 line:80%
-No one.
-No one.

00:38:07.720 --> 00:38:08.280 line:80%
No one.

00:38:14.310 --> 00:38:14.910 line:80%
Captain!

00:38:18.830 --> 00:38:19.690 line:80%
Captain, look.

00:38:22.310 --> 00:38:23.510 line:80%
What's with

00:38:24.160 --> 00:38:25.620 line:80%
this bloodstained cloth?

00:38:25.800 --> 00:38:26.720 line:80%
Explain!

00:38:28.160 --> 00:38:29.870 line:80%
Who is injured in your house?

00:38:29.950 --> 00:38:31.080 line:80%
No one is injured.

00:38:32.120 --> 00:38:33.240 line:80%
I'm a butcher.

00:38:33.470 --> 00:38:35.070 line:80%
It's a rag for wiping knives.

00:38:35.280 --> 00:38:37.430 line:80%
I just slaughtered a pig a few days ago.

00:38:38.350 --> 00:38:39.680 line:80%
A rag for wiping knives?

00:38:41.470 --> 00:38:43.030 line:80%
You two, guard the front courtyard!

00:38:43.030 --> 00:38:43.600 line:80%
The rest of you,

00:38:43.600 --> 00:38:44.330 line:80%
come with me!

00:38:51.120 --> 00:38:51.760 line:80%
Sir,

00:38:52.030 --> 00:38:55.090 line:80%
the Fan family used to make a living
by butchering pigs.

00:38:57.030 --> 00:38:58.560 line:80%
Can a young lady like you

00:38:58.870 --> 00:39:00.670 line:80%
slaughter a pig all by yourself?

00:39:02.800 --> 00:39:03.640 line:80%
Do you know

00:39:03.640 --> 00:39:05.910 line:80%
that hiding refugees is a felony,

00:39:05.990 --> 00:39:07.320 line:80%
tantamount to treason?

00:39:07.600 --> 00:39:09.460 line:80%
Your whole family could be exiled

00:39:09.470 --> 00:39:10.470 line:80%
or conscripted!

00:39:11.470 --> 00:39:12.240 line:80%
Sir,

00:39:13.280 --> 00:39:14.680 line:80%
my parents are dead.

00:39:15.910 --> 00:39:16.870 line:80%
It's just

00:39:17.200 --> 00:39:19.330 line:80%
my younger sister and me in the family.

00:39:20.910 --> 00:39:21.640 line:80%
Changyu.

00:39:22.720 --> 00:39:23.390 line:80%
Come here.

00:39:24.720 --> 00:39:26.470 line:80%
Did you really hide a refugee?

00:39:27.830 --> 00:39:29.280 line:80%
If you harbor anyone,

00:39:29.560 --> 00:39:31.760 line:80%
10 households will be punished together.

00:39:31.760 --> 00:39:33.470 line:80%
You don't want your neighbors

00:39:33.640 --> 00:39:35.640 line:80%
to suffer with you, do you?

00:39:36.430 --> 00:39:38.720 line:80%
If you hand the person over now,

00:39:38.760 --> 00:39:40.640 line:80%
I can still put in a word for you.

00:39:41.560 --> 00:39:44.160 line:80%
We'll say you were coerced by him.

00:39:58.830 --> 00:39:59.560 line:80%
Stand ready!

00:40:13.080 --> 00:40:14.680 line:80%
The soldiers have found you!

00:40:15.760 --> 00:40:16.360 line:80%
Come here.

00:40:18.400 --> 00:40:21.200 line:80%
[Fan]

00:40:18.870 --> 00:40:20.240 line:80%
Sorry, sir!

00:40:20.510 --> 00:40:22.510 line:80%
My sister and I were
playing hide-and-seek.

00:40:22.510 --> 00:40:23.990 line:80%
You came so suddenly,

00:40:24.120 --> 00:40:26.720 line:80%
and I didn't have time to call her
out of hiding.

00:40:30.280 --> 00:40:30.950 line:80%
No one.

00:40:31.760 --> 00:40:32.390 line:80%
No one.

00:40:33.990 --> 00:40:38.020 line:80%
[Fan]

00:40:35.470 --> 00:40:36.080 line:80%
All right!

00:40:36.350 --> 00:40:37.720 line:80%
Let's go check the next household!

00:40:37.720 --> 00:40:38.250 line:80%
Let's go!

00:40:44.760 --> 00:40:46.820 line:80%
You, go search the pigsty over there.

00:40:47.560 --> 00:40:48.090 line:80%
Yes, sir.

00:40:51.430 --> 00:40:53.030 line:80%
Why do I have to search this?

00:40:55.030 --> 00:40:57.290 line:80%
What is there to search in a lousy pigsty?

00:41:16.950 --> 00:41:18.760 line:80%
Sir, watch out. The pigs bite.

00:41:27.870 --> 00:41:30.870 line:80%
Sir, watch your step—
there's pig offal on the ground!

00:41:35.320 --> 00:41:37.120 line:80%
No one here! There's no one here!

00:41:37.120 --> 00:41:38.240 line:80%
Just two pigs!

00:41:37.180 --> 00:41:39.070 line:80%
[Fan]

00:41:44.640 --> 00:41:46.430 line:80%
Changning, go lock the gate.

00:41:54.470 --> 00:41:55.390 line:80%
It's me.

00:41:54.760 --> 00:42:04.660 line:80%
♪ In gold-thread dress,
with moth or willow ornaments ♪

00:42:03.160 --> 00:42:03.910 line:80%
I'm coming.

00:42:05.470 --> 00:42:15.060 line:80%
♪ Giggling, she melts into the throng
with trails of scents ♪

00:42:16.100 --> 00:42:20.800 line:80%
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

00:42:19.640 --> 00:42:20.760 line:80%
They're all gone.

00:42:20.820 --> 00:42:25.720 line:80%
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

00:42:22.760 --> 00:42:23.760 line:80%
You can relax now.

00:42:26.360 --> 00:42:28.300 line:80%
♪ When all at once I turn my head ♪

00:42:29.070 --> 00:42:31.780 line:80%
♪ I find her there ♪

00:42:32.400 --> 00:42:36.890 line:80%
♪ Where lantern light is dimly shed ♪

00:42:37.600 --> 00:42:42.200 line:80%
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

00:42:42.230 --> 00:42:47.230 line:80%
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

00:42:47.790 --> 00:42:49.920 line:80%
♪ When all at once I turn my head ♪

00:42:50.530 --> 00:42:55.020 line:80%
♪ I find her there ♪

00:42:53.680 --> 00:42:54.720 line:80%
It's okay now.

00:42:56.620 --> 00:43:06.240 line:80%
♪ Where lantern light is dimly shed ♪

00:43:11.500 --> 00:43:14.950 line:80%
[Post-Credits Scene]

00:43:17.030 --> 00:43:18.430 line:80%
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

00:43:22.700 --> 00:43:26.070 line:80%
♪ In the depths of winter, snow sweeps
across the northern wilderness ♪

00:43:24.340 --> 00:43:32.290 line:80%
[Xiangsheng Troupe]

00:43:26.900 --> 00:43:30.760 line:80%
♪ We first met in that snow
when your life hung by a thread ♪

00:43:32.370 --> 00:43:36.290 line:80%
♪ Fated by heaven, bound by two hearts ♪

00:43:36.810 --> 00:43:44.180 line:80%
♪ I vowed to wield
the butcher's knife for you ♪

00:43:40.950 --> 00:43:42.550 line:80%
Whose child is this? Get out!

00:43:43.080 --> 00:43:43.560 line:80%
Get out!

00:43:46.280 --> 00:43:48.800 line:80%
Don't come in here! Whose child is this?

00:43:46.530 --> 00:43:48.390 line:80%
♪ Hidden tides surge
as spears clash amid the chaos of war ♪

00:43:48.900 --> 00:43:51.600 line:80%
♪ Through life and death,
we remain side by side ♪

00:43:52.310 --> 00:43:55.080 line:80%
♪ She exchanges the butcher's knife
for a weapon of battle ♪

00:43:54.830 --> 00:43:55.760 line:80%
You naughty kid!

00:43:56.030 --> 00:44:05.510 line:80%
♪ A woman of valor raises her weapon
toward the battlefield ♪

00:43:56.830 --> 00:43:58.030 line:80%
Everyone, sorry about that.

00:43:58.030 --> 00:43:58.640 line:80%
Sorry.